ig's private method. There might be extra tracking for library classes, but it shouldn’t be an issue. I also need to temporarily clear dns.server/search, but I’ll remember to restore the system properties and locale afterwards with a helper using try/finally.\n\n**Evaluating test task setup**\n\nI’m figuring out that the test task likely relies on metadata. Without it for the sun, the native ResolverConfig.findSunJVM might misfire. I think that to directly findWin for getBundle, the metadata for the bundle will be essential at runtime. The agent config could come into play if there's a nativeTest following the test. The instructions I read suggest that tests should typically run under Native Image by default, which seems to indicate a nativeTest in the workflow after javaTest.\n\n**Exploring metadata options**\n\nI’m considering if I could add manual metadata reflection for a private method or field. Would that broaden the usability? It seems that this would only apply to the active class. I need to verify if we have the correct metadata syntax. This involves searching through the method entries to see what’s possible. There’s definitely some complexity here, but it could lead to improved functionality!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0daabe48e56945910169f732d5366081a29914c293bfa40944\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9zLuNe81JxclT1cPTfAkq2CvpwTxKplpi3n3rV5I9BR8nhecSzem9WryEDNVzy7C7Is6Sl0-sAxzeQC9DVyVIZkhwIvD915lvWcGliwAcfhEq9e3T0DX_xyyW3GBsviXxYU8V6vVdOopTFOE9pS_Bsf2LUQdY49oyqzT0-HM301wcBVRBkvaw5KO8g4zugNPQ-4WjmUfFVI5Ule1swqigaAUieAO3gPACT3YXM32Zaip-Zc2YDjzj2R_WJ4crpi78f1lyQfsKznO5F12Y3vEAKk-7zbzm7lBv6fVkKVa1wrU_Iejcox4rmK8sMU8E77NLV2AG7u8TiUuPsFZSsu9bn6qWNojjEVGqx4_ujK_m1AW_KLsNChAOA9I4_Q00Y9GSGPtIxPq0DrG0Rn2er7sb44eaozLPBjolaa8jkHPpLHCD9dRFinlg_RNuoEl6vRBDwLrvq8T3VzQg0n-NPITFs50cAaJkaD2PxaqYCPp47ozgz4RPW0Rx24o4ByVWBrlkBL_QhhKwawzzkO47PtHB4GqFYfa9ZT4aer0iyQIfXdmwr8L4ftHwb5PDIPb-wWmV-rT1u0-uhTug7Tl-AaKJScZemujamWXFzQ0D87YyCJePVpEiCflKZBq